text: @fedexhelp We've received a final attempt notice on a delivery while out of town last week from the Pflugerville, TX location. Called the FedEx number and got an auto voice stating to "have the recipient call and give additional information", as we were trying to do....
@FedExHelp ..... How are we supposed to give FedEx the additional info needed?

@trinityhelimd Hello, this is Robin. I'd be happy to look into this for you. Please DM your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r
@trinityhelimd Thank you. Please allow me time to view your details. I will return to you shortly. ~ Robin
